data.description: A wonderful opportunity awaits you in the heart of Bel Air MD at 922 Cheswold Court. This 3-bedroom, 3.5-bath  end-of-group townhome is nestled in a quiet culdesac offering a perfect blend of style, comfort, and convenience. The kitchen welcomes you with beautiful white cabinetry and contemporary new flooring, perfectly designed for large gatherings or intimate meals. As you step into the bright and spacious family room, you’ll feel an inviting ambiance with natural sunlight pouring through the large windows. Take a peek into the main floor half bathroom before stepping outside to your private outdoor oasis, surrounded by established landscape and views of the adjacent park. This yard is perfect for bonfires, summer grilling or a spot to grow the garden you’ve been dreaming of! As you head upstairs, the second floor welcomes you with three bedrooms and two full bathrooms. The primary suite greets you with high ceilings featuring sky lights, large closets and a private bathroom. Descend to the finished lower level, and you will find a versatile space which includes a third full bathroom, a large utility room for laundry and storage, and an open living area with new carpeting suitable for a second family room, office, or home gym. This home is not just a residence,it's a haven for outdoor entertaining and spacious living. Located just minutes from desirable downtown Bel Air, you’ll enjoy all of the conveniences town living has to offer, including close proximity to schools, shops and restaurants. Don't miss out on the chance to make  922 Cheswold Court your new home!
